  <metadata>
    <name>VIE-L3 — Semmering &amp; Rax Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from VIE and ride into the Semmering &amp; Rax. Hit Semmering Pass — 985m and Rax Cable Car Viewpoint — 1545m. Loop back to VIE over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
    <author><name>JetMyMoto</name></author>
    <time>2026-04-08T07:39:20.953Z</time>
  </metadata>
